project_descr: The project aims at strengthening the capacity of UNDP main national counterpart, the Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Cooperation, to coordinate the implementation, monitoring and evaluation of UNDP programme.

outputs.output_descr: UNDP will provide support and strengthen the capacity of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs to coordinate, implement, monitor and evaluate UNDP Country Programme, contributing for the improved management of the available resources.
